Cactus Code Thorn ScalarAnalysis
Thorn Author(s)     : Yupeng Zhang <yzhang3433@gatech.edu>
Thorn Maintainer(s) : Yupeng Zhang <yzhang3433@gatech.edu>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Purpose of the thorn: compute the radiated energy, angular momentum, and momentum of scalar field waves

dE/dt = -r^2 \int T_{tr} d\Omega 

dP^i/dt = r^2 \int T_{ir} d\Omega
